<!--Japanese-->
      <div class="education" id="jpnse">

        <h4>Japanese</h4>

        <p>I have successfully completed four semesters of intensive Japanese and hundreds
          of hours of individual study. As a complimnet to my Asian Studies Certificate, learning
          Japanese not only allows me to communicate effectively with other Japanese speakers, but
          also introduced me to cultural concepts that exist only within Japan. As such, I have a
          specialized academic concentation in Japan and Japanese culture and East Asian cultures
          more broadly.
        </p>

      </div>
<!--End Japanese-->

