<!-- Pets -->

      <div id="pet info">
        <h3>Meet my Pets!</h3>

        <p> I have a Miniature Schnauzer named Tucker and my two wonderful cats Sara (left)
          and Nyx (right). My family adopted Sara when I was very young and, ever since then,
          she has been a faithful companion throughout my life. She, along with our family dog
          Tucker, are notorious in our house for stealing food when no one is looking. Tucker
          loves chewing sticks in our backyard and is an absolute menace to the local bunny
          population, who are often chased back into their tiny dens by his shrill bark. He also
          terrorizes our youngest cat, Nyx, who prefers to hide in cabinets and under beds rather
          than encounter Tucker's playful attitude. She won't hesitate to put up a fight if he
          gets too close though! All my pets have been beloved friends and family members and
          there's never a dull moment when they're around.

        </p>

